# 22 - Data Schema Designer
# Design database schemas from requirements

NAME schema-designer
INPUT requirements_file
INPUT database DEFAULT "postgresql"
INPUT style DEFAULT "normalized"

GOAL parse "Read $requirements_file. List entities and key relationships."
GOAL design "Design $style $database schema. Essential columns only. Skip optional fields."
GOAL validate "Quick check: PKs, FKs, obvious issues. No extensive analysis."
GOAL output "Generate DDL with brief comments. Save to schema-output.sql."

RUN design USING parse, design, validate, output
